# MusicLibrarySectionRequestable

**Protocol**

A protocol for types your app uses as sections when fetching items using a library sectioned request.

## Declaration

```swift
protocol MusicLibrarySectionRequestable
```

## Conforming Types

- Album
- Artist
- Genre
- Playlist
- TitledSection
